00:21:43,620 --> 00:21:45,820
Skoro mi to nazaj ušlo.

237
00:21:45,820 --> 00:21:48,420
Bolo to naozaj dramatické.

238
00:21:48,420 --> 00:21:50,820
Pokračujme.

239
00:21:50,820 --> 00:21:53,060


240
