296
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:13,120
Vidíte ten ostrov?

297
00:26:13,120 --> 00:26:16,190
Aký ostrov?
Ste slepí?

298
00:26:16,190 --> 00:26:17,290
Prestaň!

299
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:22,860
Áno, máte pravdu.

300
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:23,990
Už mi môj zrak dobre neslúži.

301
00:26:23,990 --> 00:26:26,460
Hlúpi bastardi.

302
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:29,520
Poďme.

303
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:36,290
Okrem toho,
polovica z vášho

304
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:38,820
úlovku pôjde vždy môjmu šéfovi.

305
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:40,690
- Rozumiete?
- Pravdaže.

306
00:26:41,260 --> 00:26:44,260
- Dobre!
- To som rád.

307
00:26:44,990 --> 00:26:46,090
Zbohom!

308
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:52,620
Zbohom!

309
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:58,760
Sme bohatí!

310
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:01,020
Poďme.

311
