Ďakujem ti, Bože.

333
00:29:35,460 --> 00:29:37,190
Ten malý...

334
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:39,090
Ah Mo Gae.

335
00:29:39,890 --> 00:29:42,260
To ty si Gil Dong?

336
00:29:56,960 --> 00:30:01,060
Prečo na mňa tak zazeráš?!

337
