- Odmena?
- Zachránte ma!

426
00:36:15,290 --> 00:36:16,630
Ty malý...

427
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:33,420
Ak budete mať toto pri sebe,

428
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:35,920
prinesie vám to veľké šťastie.

