571
00:46:49,190 --> 00:46:51,020
Otec možno zomrie.

572
00:46:51,120 --> 00:46:52,990
Prečo by mal zomrieť?

573
00:46:52,990 --> 00:46:54,820
So Bu Ri povedal,

574
